+│  - requestRecipesForAiDishes()                    │
+│  - isAiSuggestionRelevant()                       │
+└──────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
+                   │
+┌──────────────────▼────────────────────────────────┐
+│         BUSINESS LOGIC LAYER                       │
+│    (ScanFoodLocalMatcher - local matching)        │
+│  - findUncoveredIngredients()                     │
+│  - suggestDishes() / suggestDishesRelaxed()       │
