+| `isAiSuggestionRelevant: >= 2` | 2 | Min matched for multi-ingredient |
+| `isAiSuggestionRelevant: >= 50%` | 0.5 | Min coverage for 3+ ingredients |
+| `isAiSuggestionRelevant: single-ingredient` | 5 | Max allowed missing for 1 ingredient |
